reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I've never had a dish drainer so clever. It's narrow, so it fits nicely on my counter. The draining trough extends so that you can back the dish drainer away from your sink and still drain water from your dishes. The knife and tableware holder is great for knives and holding those small things that always get lost before. The cup holder will not hold American size glasses and mugs, but it's useful for holding and protecting many other items - small plates, measuring cups and small jars. I've never loved a drainer before until now. Call me silly, but it's just that cleverly designed.
